  "title": "Delivery Driver (Class 3, Lorry)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title: </strong>Delivery Driver (Class 3, Lorry)<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Yishun, Singapore<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br /><strong>Working Days and Hours: </strong>6 Days, Monday - Saturday (730AM - 530PM)<br /><br /><strong>Job Summary:</strong><br />We are looking for a reliable and responsible Delivery Driver to transport goods to customers safely. The ideal candidate will have a valid driver’s license, excellent time management skills, and a commitment to providing exceptional customer service.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Load, transport, and deliver goods to customers promptly and in excellent condition.</li><li>Follow assigned routes and time schedules.</li><li>Review orders before and after delivery to ensure accuracy and customer satisfaction.</li><li>Maintain communication with dispatch and report any issues or delays.</li><li>Adhere to all traffic laws and safety regulations.</li><li>Keep the delivery vehicle clean and in good working condition.</li><li>Assist in packing in chiller room to when necessary.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Valid class 3 driver’s license with a clean driving record.</li><li>Proven experience as a delivery driver or similar role.</li><li>Strong organizational and time management skills.</li><li>Excellent customer service and communication skills.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in handling perishable goods.</li><li>Knowledge of the local area and efficient routes.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary and incentives.</li><li>Career growth opportunities.</li></ul><p>If you are a motivated and dependable individual with a passion for delivering excellent service, we encourage you to apply!<br /></p>",
